  METHOD render_reviews.

    DATA: lt_list   TYPE zif_aor_types=>ty_review_tt,
          lo_review TYPE REF TO zcl_aor_review.

    FIELD-SYMBOLS: <ls_list> LIKE LINE OF lt_list.


    lt_list = zcl_aor_service=>list( ).

